summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed, including:  
  - Ratification of prior Tranche 1 Placement Shares (99.5% approval).  
  - Approval for Tranche 2 Placement Shares (99.2% approval).  
  - Director participation in Placement (Justin Barton: 98.7%; Roger Steinepries: 98.3%).  
  - Conversion of accrued directors’ fees to shares (98.4–98.9% approval).  

*No material trading or capital markets impact identified beyond routine governance approvals.*
